dc_title_s: Bourdelois, pays de Medoc, et la prevoste de Born
dc_description_s: 1 map ; 38 x 49 cm.|Relief shown pictorially.|North oriented to the left.|Includes a decorative cartouche with grapes and vines, compass rose, and illustrations of ships on the ocean.|This state was published in atlases by Jan Jansson in 1631, 1631-33, 1633, 1636, and 1637.|From the Jansson Appendix Atlas 1636-1680, title created to represent a unique collection within the Clark Library, University of Michigan.
